<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/lammy-review/about> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Lammy Review, chaired by David Lammy MP, is an independent review of the treatment of, and outcomes for, Black, Asian and Minority Ethnic (BAME) individuals in the Criminal Justice System (CJS)."@en .
